<div id="review_2437325056" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2437325056" />
    <a title="Aya" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/21632198-aya"><img alt="Aya" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1535796956p2/21632198.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2437325056?book_show_action=true">Jun 27, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Aya" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Aya" href="/user/show/21632198-aya">Aya</a>
      </span>

          added it




        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2437325056" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7774673467856776508">I thought blind faith was bad, but what&apos;s worse is trying to prove garbage ideologies with scientific concepts you don&apos;t fully comprehend. I would have given it one star but that&apos;s way too much credit for the author. Mustafa Mahmoud is a fraud. He&apos;s a failed physician and a failed artist. Arab Muslims give him undeserving credit because he panders to their already set in stone beliefs. This book was a waste of time.</span>
  <span id="freeText7774673467856776508" style="display:none">I thought blind faith was bad, but what's worse is trying to prove garbage ideologies with scientific concepts you don't fully comprehend. I would have given it one star but that's way too much credit for the author. Mustafa Mahmoud is a fraud. He's a failed physician and a failed artist. Arab Muslims give him undeserving credit because he panders to their already set in stone beliefs. This book was a waste of time.</span>
  <a data-text-id="7774673467856776508" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


