<div id="review_1499929092" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1499929092" />
    <a title="ɑƨħŵɑɡ ♥Team Magnus Damora FOREVER♥" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4676971-team-magnus-damora-forever"><img alt="ɑƨħŵɑɡ ♥Team Magnus Damora FOREVER♥" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1390251598p2/4676971.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1499929092?book_show_action=true">Jan 07, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="ɑƨħŵɑɡ ♥Team Magnus Damora FOREVER♥" class="user" itemprop="url" name="ɑƨħŵɑɡ ♥Team Magnus Damora FOREVER♥" href="/user/show/4676971-team-magnus-damora-forever">ɑƨħŵɑɡ ♥Team Magnus Damora FOREVER♥</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4676971-team-magnus-damora-forever?shelf=%D8%AB%D9%82%D8%A7%D9%81%D8%A9-%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%85%D8%A9-%D8%AA%D9%86%D9%85%D9%8A%D8%A9-%D8%B0%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8A%D8%A9">ثقافة-عامة-تنمية-ذاتية</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4676971-team-magnus-damora-forever?shelf=misc">misc</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4676971-team-magnus-damora-forever?shelf=religious">religious</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4676971-team-magnus-damora-forever?shelf=2016-newyears-resolution-kickstart">2016-newyears-resolution-kickstart</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4676971-team-magnus-damora-forever?shelf=2016-reads">2016-reads</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1499929092" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14427876469931418091">After my first book for this author called &quot;my journey from doubt to faith&quot; I decided to go for this one as well since I was blown away with the easy and heart-warming writing style.<br/><br/>This one is called &quot;a dialogue with an atheist&quot; is an imaginary dialogue, <s>which I thought was real</s> between the writer and an atheist. Which is counterproductive right? Well, the writer&apos;s intention is to explain some of the most common statements atheists come up with when it comes to Islamic religion. He did a good j</span>
  <span id="freeText14427876469931418091" style="display:none">After my first book for this author called "my journey from doubt to faith" I decided to go for this one as well since I was blown away with the easy and heart-warming writing style.<br /><br />This one is called "a dialogue with an atheist" is an imaginary dialogue, <s>which I thought was real</s> between the writer and an atheist. Which is counterproductive right? Well, the writer's intention is to explain some of the most common statements atheists come up with when it comes to Islamic religion. He did a good job with some questions and explanations but needed to explain more about others.<br /><br />I respect this man's knowledge and I've enjoyed his science series back when I was a child. But of course, some of his views are outdated and for those who have read more about Islam probably won't benefit from this. However, it is still good for an atheist research starter-pack.</span>
  <a data-text-id="14427876469931418091" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


